<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white p-3 md:p-6"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <div class="space-y-6">
    <p class="font-bold text-gray-700">Segna con una <strong>X</strong> le risposte corrette.</p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <!-- Colonna sinistra -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <!-- Domanda 1 -->
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-3">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(1) %>
            Per andare a scuola, Alessandro percorre ogni mattina 395 metri. Quanti chilometri percorre?
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>3,95 km</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>39,5 km</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>395 km</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
              <span>0,395 km</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Domanda 2 -->
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-3">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(2) %>
            Quanto può misurare il lato più lungo del tuo sussidiario?
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
              <span>29 cm</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span><span class="whitespace-nowrap">2 900 dm</span></span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>0,29 dam</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>2,9 m</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Domanda 3 -->
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-3">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(3) %>
            Quanti decagrammi corrispondono a 1,72 decigrammi?
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>17,2 dag</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>172 dag</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>0,172 dag</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
              <span>0,0172 dag</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Domanda 4 -->
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-3">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(4) %>
            Quale fra i seguenti risultati è esatto?
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2 text-center font-bold">9 hg + 45 g = .......... g</p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>45,09 g</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>45,9 g</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>54 g</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
              <span>945 g</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Domanda 5 -->
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-3">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(5) %>
            Matteo beve ogni giorno 1,5 ℓ di acqua. La mamma gli compra 30 bottigliette di acqua da 50 cℓ l'una. Per quanti giorni basterà l'acqua a Matteo?
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
              <span>10 giorni</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>5 giorni</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>15 giorni</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>20 giorni</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Domanda 6 -->
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-3">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(6) %>
            Quale tra le seguenti equivalenze NON è corretta?
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>359 cm = 3,59 m</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span><span class="whitespace-nowrap">1 300 g</span> = 1,3 kg</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
              <span>89 daℓ = 890 dℓ</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>0,08 km = 8 dam</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Colonna destra -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <!-- Domanda 7 -->
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-3">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(7) %>
            Il peso di una cesta piena di pane è di <span class="whitespace-nowrap">6 550 g</span>. La cesta vuota pesa <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: 1, den: 5 %> del peso lordo. Quanto pesa il pane?
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span><span class="whitespace-nowrap">6 000 g</span></span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span><span class="whitespace-nowrap">1 310 g</span></span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
              <span><span class="whitespace-nowrap">5 240 g</span></span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span><span class="whitespace-nowrap">7 860 g</span></span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Domanda 8 -->
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-3">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(8) %>
            Nel suo salvadanaio Luca ha una banconota da € 200, due da € 50, tre da € 10, due monete da € 1 e una moneta da 50 centesimi. Quanti soldi ha Luca in totale?
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>€ 261,50</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>€ 334</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
              <span>€ 332,50</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>€ 333,50</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Domanda 9 -->
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-3">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(9) %>
            In cartoleria Samuele compra 3 gomme uguali. Paga con una banconota da € 10 e riceve € 6,40 di resto. Quanto costa una gomma?
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>€ 0,64</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
              <span>€ 1,20</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>€ 3,60</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>€ 1,40</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Domanda 10 -->
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-3">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(10) %>
            Serena ha comprato 7,5 hg di prosciutto che costa € 15 al chilogrammo. Quanto ha speso?
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>€ 7,50</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>€ 22,50</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
              <span>€ 11,25</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>€ 22,25</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Domanda 11 -->
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-3">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(11) %>
            Quale fra le seguenti formule risolve il problema?
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">Paolo ha rivenduto la sua collezione di giornalini a € 40. Se aveva pagato € 43,50 per l'acquisto di tutti i giornalini, qual è stata la sua perdita?</p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>Ricavo – Spesa</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
              <span>Spesa – Ricavo</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>Spesa – Guadagno</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>Ricavo + Spesa</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
  </div>
</div>
